{
  "stem": "2735.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] so we had all those people coming in to us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they didn't live all with us.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We took in one family and some single man that for awhile stayed with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But that wasn't bothering me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I mean, comfort, like with other things that are important today, didn't mean much to us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And my mother all of a sudden was very strong.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And as I said, she used to make meals.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And a lot of those refugees were having the meals with us.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] I still remember preparing for Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody was in shul when I and my girlfriend were going from one house to the other one.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were fasting and preparing all that good food on the table.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We knew we can't touch it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But I saw that all our friends are not religious anymore.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I saw them eating on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I was working on Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I had to come into the office.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] for a while, it really shook me up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "I mean, all that approach that-- that-- religion is the opium of the masses and that everything-- and the theory of Darwinism is God and all that stuff.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Life was not as happy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And-- but as far as things to get, we weren't lacking too much because we had relatives that-- on the small towns and they used to send us everything.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "All kind of-- and it wasn't kosher anymore.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "They used to send us salamis and all kind of meats and all kind of stuff.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
